summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds to portions of Blocks 377, 391, 409, 423 and 425 of Seattle Tide Lands, portions of Section 13, Township 24 North, Range 3 East W.M. and a portion of Section 18, Township 24 North, Range 4 East W.M. for Overhead Bridge and General Municipal Purposes and placing them under the jurisdiction of the Engineering Department (West Seattle Bridge Replacement Project; RW 7855).
